## 自定义QML组件

新建QML文件-`TimerDateLabel.qml`
```QML
import QtQuick 2.14
import QtQuick.Controls 1.4

Label {
    id:label
    Timer {
        interval: 500; running: true; repeat: true
        onTriggered: label.text = Date().toString()
    }
}
```
在`main.qml`中调用`TimerDateLabel.qml`
```QML
import QtQuick 2.14
import QtQuick.Window 2.14
import QtQuick.Controls 1.4

Window {
    width: 640
    height: 480
    visible: true
    title: qsTr("Hello World")

    Item{
        anchors.fill: parent

        Column{
            TimerDateLable{
              color: "red"
            }
            TimerDateLable{
              color: "blue
            }
    }

}
}
```
